# =============================================================================
# AsliChoice — .env.example
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This file lists ALL environment variables introduced across the monorepo.
# Each module/agent appends its own variables in subsequent plan steps.
#
# NOTE: Real `.env` files are NEVER committed. In production/staging they live
#       under `~/deploy_config/<env>/` on the deploy host and are symlinked or
#       sourced by `deploy.sh`. For local development, copy this file to
#       `.env` at the appropriate location and fill in real values.
# =============================================================================

